{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, the comparison between YOLOv8 and CNN-RCNN for classification demonstrated an accuracy of about 96%.",
    "This suggests a promising avenue for utilizing deep learning models in UAV-based forest fire detection systems, showcasing their potential for high-accuracy early fire recognition.",
    "Further refinements and field implementations could lead to more robust and effective real-time fire monitoring systems.",
